<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Acroterion fragment from a <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> lid</rs> <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.32</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.25</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.245</measure> with a <rs type="decoration">relief</rs> of <rs type="decoration">Ganymede</rs> and the <rs type="decoration">eagle</rs>, broken away above.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Below, a simple moulding, <rs type="execution" key="scalpro">inscribed</rs> in one line on the upper fascia, which is broken to the left and worn to the right.</p>
